OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778875555
OL,3,CCouncil to fine and prosecute people
OL,4,Cputting up England flags
OL,6,FShropshire Council is looking to
OL,7,Fprosecute anyone deemed to have
OL,8,Fattached flags to lampposts without
OL,9,Fpermission.
OL,11,FSt George's Cross and Union flags have
OL,12,Fbeen put up across Shrewsbury, as well
OL,13,Fas across the country - in what
OL,14,Fcritics have called a sign of anti-
OL,15,Fimmigration.
OL,17,FShropshire Council has said it would
OL,18,Fremove "unauthorised flags" and charge
OL,19,Fthose responsible for the costs.
OL,26,@zD@HOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778875555
OL,3,CCouncil to fine and prosecute people
OL,4,Cputting up England flags
OL,6,FThe local authority has said a rise in
OL,7,Freports of abuse, harassment and
OL,8,Fintimidation made against residents,
OL,9,Fstaff (including contractors) and
OL,10,Fcouncillors has impacted the pace at
OL,11,Fwhich the council can remove the flags.
OL,13,FCouncillor David Vasmer, who is in
OL,14,Fcharge of roads and the environment at
OL,15,Fthe authority, said they are looking
OL,16,Fto prosecute anyone who has affixed
OL,17,Fanything without authority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778875555
OL,3,CCouncil to fine and prosecute people
OL,4,Cputting up England flags
OL,6,F"Removing flags is not normal council
OL,7,Fbusiness, it is not a statutory
OL,8,Fservice, and therefore it comes at an
OL,9,Fadditional cost to the council and its
OL,10,Fresidents, depending on the number and
OL,11,Flocation of flags," said Councillor
OL,12,FVasmer.
OL,14,F"We plan to remove all unauthorised
OL,15,Fflags from our street lighting columns
OL,16,Fand other highway assets. This will be
OL,17,Fin Shrewsbury initially with plans to
OL,18,Fremove all unauthorised flags across
OL,19,Fthe county in time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]{D@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778875555
OL,3,CCouncil to fine and prosecute people
OL,4,Cputting up England flags
OL,6,FHe added: "Putting up the Union Flag
OL,7,Fis not a hate crime, and we have never
OL,8,Fsuggested that it is. What we do not,
OL,9,Fhowever, support is the unauthorised
OL,10,Fattachment of flags or any other
OL,11,Fobjects to street lighting columns,
OL,12,Fhighway infrastructure or other public
OL,13,Fstreet furniture due to health and
OL,14,Fsafety issues, damage and costs to
OL,15,Fresidents, nor do we support or
OL,16,Ftolerate the abuse of our staff and
OL,17,Fmembers.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778875555
OL,3,CCouncil to fine and prosecute people
OL,4,Cputting up England flags
OL,6,F"In addition, we have been working
OL,7,Fwith partners and have put a bid into
OL,8,Fthe Home Office for funds to support
OL,9,Fengagement with all our communities
OL,10,Faround community safety and cohesion
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"We have also requested funds to
OL,14,Fsupport the development of local
OL,15,Fflags, designed for and with our
OL,16,Fcommunities, including our young
OL,17,Fpeople, that relate to our heritage
OL,18,Fand communities. These flags to be put
OL,19,Fup alongside the appropriate display
OL,20,Fof the Union flag and St George's
OL,21,Fflag."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU}D@FO]
